column3: NSLOCTEXT("", "034D07B44DE07AA5AF2EECA7A7575803", "Well, that was something, wasn\'t it it? Good work, team!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "6ED40FE949A01078845AF482D6E988F8", "I knew that the ocean would get it! You didn\'t believe me, but now look what happened!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "46959414427B96CAA1B26989CDCE33B1", "I just want to find my sister okay?! She would believe me!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "E0EE42FE4FBD97559593719CF1E60577", "We\'ll be pals in no time, you\'ll see!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "45EED998459BB1E1F356B0B5F168D834", "We\'re all here for you, okay? Together we\'ll find your sister in no time.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "813F0ACB454E8C7AFEB673B1E2DC45CA", "I guess you guys aren\'t TERRIBLE. I\'ll let you travel with me for now.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "86BF456B4B4830579847839F4BDA287D", "Come on, we have a sister to find!")
